<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-CDDC2569-412F-48C5-90F2-541539FA0EE2" version="1" lang="en-US"?><concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-CDDC2569-412F-48C5-90F2-541539FA0EE2" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic concept)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c concept oceConcept-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">21 The function of the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp></title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-34C6A3E5-E809-4139-80CC-275A8CCF9EDC"><p class="- topic/p ">What is the function of the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp>? 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Definition</ph></title><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp> manages the Power and Print data in the Colorado system. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-3225DD38-160F-42B4-A279-10AA00359615" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Functional Block diagram</title><fig id="GUID-621C0FBE-A753-4A2A-A1D0-4B4DFC47C616" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C4CE382E-D15E-4F03-AC6C-03B4CAC8090B-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C4CE382E-D15E-4F03-AC6C-03B4CAC8090B-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_149E42233D224948A977D6176630ADAC" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Power management</title><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp> uses <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">On/off button</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 24S8 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">FRA_SOFT_ON_SW</compsignal></comp> to determine if the Colorado system has to be switched ON or OFF. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp> uses the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">AC Switch</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA01 </compcodenr></comp> to switch the power supplies in the system ON and OFF. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The power supplies involved : 
</p><ul id="UL_85B3B1B7FBBF46CD8FE45CD9B0BF4899" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_187B9FFB6C0043E3B88AA4A9F1E6867C" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">24 VDC Supply</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22G02 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">P_24V_1</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_E8668B1E420C4699BD5A32CA63BDF5DB" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">36 VDC Supply</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22G03 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">P_36_1</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_32E91C2784C643658AE8ECA4A20B4614" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">48 VDC Supply Curing</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22G04 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">48V_CUR/1</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_50D706A455C94E76BFA6522FC2A55A9E" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">49.5 VDC Supply Printhead</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22G05 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">49.5V_PH</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">The DRC PBA receives feed back signals from <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA02 </compcodenr></comp> and <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Printhead Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> that are used to check if the power supplies switched on correctly. 
</p></section><section id="SECTION_71E989E6452D49ECA0FD59DA52400594" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Print data management / transfer</title><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp> send all print data to the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Carriage PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 05PBA07 </compcodenr></comp> via an optical connection. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This print data is received from <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Embedded controller PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA03 </compcodenr></comp>. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-1070FD93-CFAD-4011-8EAB-1BB9341AD686" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Connections</title><p class="- topic/p ">Main connections on the PBA: 
</p><ul id="UL_688418EB04B84F728FAC5AD0625F9EA5" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_9E63897CB22244CCB4C3A74A3520D4E7" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Carriage PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 05PBA07 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_7BB2BBFBA2DA489A889F718D214403CA" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">On/off button</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 24S8 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">FRA_SOFT_ON_SW</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_E2D480F8098F4C0E95206277A37E186E" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">AC Switch</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA01 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_4F435CD1D7B941A082459D8CB0415436" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA02 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_E9E147232EE8400A9B3376D3690F3557" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Printhead Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></li><li id="LI_3C1DA3DBE5F84910923853336369EDE2" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Embedded controller PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></li></ul></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-0AFDBAB0-4E30-4BC0-AA0D-6AC80B191C49.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Functional description</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
